@JonathonReinhart Also, note that I was specifically having trouble with _unnamed_ structures.

```
typedef struct {
    int myMember;
} MyStruct;
```

As opposed to named structures with a typedef.

```
struct MyStruct {
    int myMember;
};

typedef struct MyStruct MyStruct;
```

I didn't see any reference in your issue so I'm not sure which case you are working with.

